No, from an internet cafe...
where people meet and gather and such.

12
00:01:00,610 --> 00:01:06,089
I know all of Ji Hyun's friends,
and I don't remember her mentioning you.

13
00:01:06,090 --> 00:01:11,659
Your wedding anniversary last year...
in April or May,

14
00:01:11,660 --> 00:01:15,829
Ji Hyun showed you some magic
with tissue flying,

15
00:01:15,830 --> 00:01:19,550
mom's necklace in one hand
and dad's cufflinks in the other.

16
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:21,860
Yes.

17
00:01:21,870 --> 00:01:24,299
<i>Shin Ji Hyun, don't be obvious.</i>

18
00:01:24,300 --> 00:01:27,810
<i>You're Ji Hyun's friend, not her.</i>

19
00:01:28,470 --> 00:01:31,589
She had practiced that with me a lot.

20
00:01:31,590 --> 00:01:32,819
Did she?

21
00:01:32,820 --> 00:01:37,079
I apologize for coming
when Ji Hyun's like this.

22
00:01:37,080 --> 00:01:42,079
You knew about Ji Hyun?
Who did you hear it from?

23
00:01:42,080 --> 00:01:47,340
From a college friend of Ji Hyun's.

24
00:01:48,410 --> 00:01:53,919
Oh, this is Shin Ji Hyun's doll.
The one she got from Minho.

25
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:57,629
Our Ji Hyun told you that as well?

26
00:01:57,630 --> 00:02:02,270
Of course. It was her first birthday present
when they started dating.

27
00:02:03,950 --> 00:02:12,699
How could she not have mentioned you once
when she confided so many things to you?

28
00:02:12,700 --> 00:02:19,140
Probably because we met online...
I was more like a shadow friend.

29
00:02:19,170 --> 00:02:22,840
Shin Ji Hyun has so many friends.

30
00:02:25,770 --> 00:02:29,019
But, what were you looking for?

31
00:02:29,020 --> 00:02:30,980
I'll look for it.

32
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:34,530
There will be too many CDs to look through.

33
00:02:35,350 --> 00:02:37,580
If that's all right with you.

34
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:41,070
You look like you're hurting.

35
00:02:43,620 --> 00:02:45,259
Will you do that?

36
00:02:45,260 --> 00:02:49,070
Yes. Shall I take these up as well?

37
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,830
Sure.

38
00:02:52,500 --> 00:02:54,870
<i>Why aren't you answering the phone!</i>

39
00:02:54,910 --> 00:02:59,230
<i>The kangaroo doll... you're positive
Ji Hyun's mother took it home with her?</i>

40
00:02:59,250 --> 00:03:02,150
<i>Ji Hyun's seal is in it!</i>

41
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:52,440
I'm borrowing it. Not stealing it.

42
00:04:39,690 --> 00:04:41,420
This is it.

43
00:04:41,900 --> 00:04:44,850
Okay. Take it with you.

44
00:04:45,290 --> 00:04:51,780
Please eat something. You're so thin...
Shin Ji Hyun would be so sad.

45
00:05:04,490 --> 00:05:08,600
Shin Ji Hyun loved you so much.

46
00:05:13,610 --> 00:05:16,530
Ji Hyun said that?

47
00:05:16,620 --> 00:05:20,829
Of course. She always said that...

48
00:05:20,830 --> 00:05:23,910
