before she left. She looked so thin.

110
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:59,359
Ji Hyun's friend? Did someone come by?

111
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:02,340
Didn't you see her as you came in?

112
00:11:02,510 --> 00:11:03,469
No.

113
