668
01:02:03,490 --> 01:02:04,599
<i>Let's go.</i>

669
01:02:04,600 --> 01:02:06,590
Okay.

670
01:02:13,120 --> 01:02:14,670
Go ahead.

671
01:02:18,800 --> 01:02:20,950
What did Song Yi Kyung do before this?

672
01:02:21,170 --> 01:02:22,440
Why?

673
01:02:22,570 --> 01:02:25,180
Are you in a relationship with her?

674
01:02:26,860 --> 01:02:30,700
No, she's just a part-timer.

675
01:02:32,590 --> 01:02:34,190
Then fire her.

676
01:02:34,690 --> 01:02:35,249
What?

677
01:02:35,250 --> 01:02:40,410
Why use someone who makes
customers uncomfortable?

678
01:02:40,520 --> 01:02:42,580
I'll have to train her again.

679
01:02:43,350 --> 01:02:44,670
Here.

680
01:02:45,030 --> 01:02:47,209
You said she's someone whose
circumstances you're trying to improve.

681
01:02:47,210 --> 01:02:48,329
What are her circumstances?

682
01:02:48,330 --> 01:02:50,540
That's her private life.

683
01:02:50,660 --> 01:02:52,550
You're quite strange.

684
01:02:52,650 --> 01:02:55,680
Is she your friend, a lover?

685
01:02:55,750 --> 01:02:57,489
Why not tell me if she's just a part-timer?

686
01:02:57,490 --> 01:03:01,400
Even a part-timer
has a personal life and pride.

687
01:03:02,310 --> 01:03:06,840
You're being so unlike yourself, why?

688
01:03:06,890 --> 01:03:07,819
What about me?

689
01:03:07,820 --> 01:03:11,060
You're usually such a cold person.

690
01:03:11,190 --> 01:03:14,100
But you're not to her... why?

691
01:03:19,560 --> 01:03:26,339
Ji Hyun being in the state she's in,
I feel bad to her and you for saying this,

692
01:03:26,340 --> 01:03:28,709
