698
01:03:47,880 --> 01:03:50,419
So why do something so unlike you?

699
01:03:50,420 --> 01:03:54,120
Going overboard and being overly sensitive.

700
01:03:56,000 --> 01:03:58,610
I'm not saying you really...

701
01:04:02,450 --> 01:04:04,139
Did you call me here to say this?

702
01:04:04,140 --> 01:04:06,109
- No, but...
- Then let's talk later.

703
01:04:06,110 --> 01:04:07,950
My mood is wretched.

704
01:04:25,520 --> 01:04:29,300
<i>Hyung, you acting this way...
