708
01:04:39,970 --> 01:04:42,990
<i>I... that woman?</i>

709
01:04:46,610 --> 01:04:48,210
You startled me.

710
01:05:00,150 --> 01:05:02,060
You offend me.

711
01:05:02,800 --> 01:05:05,369
Song Yi Kyung,
